{"tid":2171714,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港變「中國製造」延45天實施 港官員：向美方爭取用中國香港","createTime":"2020-08-24T06:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T09:27:10.000Z","uid":28765,"like":18,"dislike":203,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"d56ae27f32d4c53b6d781f6e8938e04b95000e1d","tid":2171714,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:45:27.000Z","msg":"2020-08-24 14:20:01<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國對香港祭出多項制裁和限制措施，包含自9月25日起，出口美國的香港商品，原產地要改為「中國」。香港商務及經濟發展局長邱騰華今（24日）表示，美方已應業界要求，將此措施延後45天，至11月9月才實施，又稱將港府正爭取改標「中國香港」等解決方式。<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n邱騰華批評，美國的政策「來意不善」，既沒有必要，也沒有理由，只是為要打擊香港的獨立關稅區地位。<br />\n<br />\n港府日前表示，美國此舉已違反世界貿易組織（WTO）規範，香港將向WTO提出申訴<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3269727\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3269727&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzsje9V6YwtzhhzuTx9UUfAJc%3D&h=ec472f44\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3269727&h=6e4c6101\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3269727</a>"},{"pid":"630d5269b97377de074cc2b0af8f10ae89a050ed","tid":2171714,"uid":29153,"like":56,"dislike":0,"score":56,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:46:13.000Z","msg":"找到了G點"},{"pid":"967258d2c05d1f6436ebb3ad4e13d25c063c2aae","tid":2171714,"uid":39010,"like":232,"dislike":3,"score":229,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:46:43.000Z","msg":"中國就中國 中國香港<br />\n又搞港獨 屌你老母<br />\n國安唔撚做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06ace2c02967ce5fe24bc53933a0c465e713b928","tid":2171714,"uid":53524,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:47:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b48f1c2f13356d2b7bcb3f21dfcf29e03d4dc16b","tid":2171714,"uid":14918,"like":48,"dislike":1,"score":47,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T06:47:46.000Z","msg":"人大改基本法腐乳可以用全港18區做生產地囉<br />\nMade in Tai Po, Made in Kowloon West